    fonts may be shared and improved in partnership\r\nwith others.\r\n\r\nThe OFL
    allows the licensed fonts to be used, studied, modified and\r\nredistributed
    freely as long as they are not sold by themselves. The\r\nfonts, including any
    derivative works, can be bundled, embedded, \r\nredistributed and/or sold with
